text: Kalimullino () is a rural locality (a village) in Novochebenkinsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 74 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 22 km from Isyangulovo, 3 km from Ishemgul. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Kalimullino
